source is likely a WD, one source could either be a WD or\nBD candidate, and the remaining two sources agree with being BD candidates. For\nonly one source no optical counterpart could be detected, which makes this\nsource a good BD candidate. We conclude that we found in total four good BD\ncandidates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2015 20:40:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Jun 2015 21:37:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 22:47:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
