iometric\nanalyses. They also provide researchers with useful, interactive tools to\ndiscover both relevant older work as well as new developments, for instance in\nthemes related to Sleeping Beauties that are also Sleeping Innovations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2015 10:37:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
