ability. Finally, the transition between travelling waves and non-uniform\nsteady states is explored as the suction amplitude increases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2015 13:24:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
